Compact 3D Models

Tired of juggling large photo files? Our app turns your room photos into a lightweight 3D point cloud, making it easy to share and store. Get a full 3D view of your space without the bulk — it’s fast, efficient, and perfect for seamless sharing with clients or friends. Simplify your workflow and experience your space in 3D today!

Experience Your Space in a New Dimension"

With the 3D point cloud, you don’t just look at a series of images — you get a fully interactive view of the room. It’s a smarter, more efficient way to share room designs or floor plans. Forget the hassle of managing multiple photos, and experience the power of 3D visualization with just a few clicks.
